{"parentUuid":"57d3ed64-4779-4ef2-8285-9f6480753d31","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/kokoax/.ghq/src/github.com/voyagegroup/ecnavi-aws-cloudformation","sessionId":"2a8f4761-430c-433e-85ef-427d6fb97e04","version":"1.0.53","message":{"id":"msg_01WufKtEZge3AzVKgRC1WLpG","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"claude-sonnet-4-20250514","content":[{"type":"text","text":"GitHub APIを使用してプルリクエストを取得できない理由はいくつか考えられます：\n\n1. **認証の問題**: GitHub APIアクセスに必要な認証が設定されていない可能性があります\n2. **権限の問題**: 該当のリポジトリへのアクセス権限がない可能性があります\n3. **PR番号の誤り**: PR #4389が存在しないか、間違った番号の可能性があります\n4. **リポジトリのプライベート設定**: プライベートリポジトリで適切なアクセス権限がない可能性があります\n\n代替案として、ローカルのリポジトリで該当のPRの変更内容を確認することもできます。git logやgit showコマンドを使用して、PR #4389に関連するコミットを探すことは可能でしょうか？"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":4,"cache_creation_input_tokens":314,"cache_read_input_tokens":28952,"output_tokens":250,"service_tier":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CRC7G15fHdD5ftxpLjFeN","type":"assistant","uuid":"62b3331c-ad0e-4681-8f5f-1ee553b2d163","timestamp":"2025-07-17T06:21:42.584Z"}
{"parentUuid":"62b3331c-ad0e-4681-8f5f-1ee553b2d163","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/kokoax/.ghq/src/github.com/voyagegroup/ecnavi-aws-cloudformation","sessionId":"2a8f4761-430c-433e-85ef-427d6fb97e04","version":"1.0.53","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"githubのfine-granted tokenの設定の例を教えてください"},"uuid":"71de134a-2ee0-4d41-b656-be0d53f831e5","timestamp":"2025-07-17T06:22:05.975Z"}
{"parentUuid":"71de134a-2ee0-4d41-b656-be0d53f831e5","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/kokoax/.ghq/src/github.com/voyagegroup/ecnavi-aws-cloudformation","sessionId":"2a8f4761-430c-433e-85ef-427d6fb97e04","version":"1.0.53","message":{"id":"msg_01Q7TMCwnqeF819A6RFuCVSW","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"claude-sonnet-4-20250514","content":[{"type":"text","text":"GitHub Fine-grained Personal Access Token の設定例を説明します：\n\n## 1. トークンの作成場所\n- GitHub → Settings → Developer settings → Personal access tokens → Fine-grained tokens\n\n## 2. 基本設定\n```\nToken name: claude-code-token\nExpiration: 90 days (推奨)\nResource owner: 自分のアカウントまたは組織\n```\n\n## 3. Repository access\n```\nSelected repositories: \n- voyagegroup/ecnavi-aws-cloudformation\n```\n\n## 4. 必要な権限（Permissions）\n### Repository permissions:\n```\n- Contents: Read and write\n- Pull requests: Read and write  \n- Issues: Read and write\n- Metadata: Read\n- Actions: Read (workflow関連で必要な場合)\n```\n\n### Account permissions:\n```\n- Git SSH keys: Read (必要に応じて)\n```\n\n## 5. 設定方法\n作成したトークンを環境変数に設定：\n```bash\nexport GITHUB_TOKEN=\"ghp_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx\"\n```\n\nまたは `~/.gitconfig` に追加：\n```\n[github]\n    token = ghp_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx\n```\n\nこれらの権限でClaudeのGitHub MCPツールが正常に動作するはずです。"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":4,"cache_creation_input_tokens":271,"cache_read_input_tokens":29266,"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CRC7JJh85j3LoGdAEi1rH","type":"assistant","uuid":"ab915fd4-7162-4e1e-abfe-74194b7a12c4","timestamp":"2025-07-17T06:22:17.014Z"}
